THE

FAIR VALUE ADJUSTMENTS TO THE ACQUIRED CLAIMS AND CLAIM ADJUSTMENT EXPENSE RESERVES AND REINSURANCE RECOVERABLES AS OF APRIL 1, 2004, THE MERGER DATE, ARE REPORTED AS OTHER

