ALSO APPROXIMATED THEIR FAIR VALUES. FAIR VALUE IS DETERMINED USING VARIOUS METHODS INCLUDING DISCOUNTED CASH FLOWS, AS APPROPRIATE FOR THE VARIOUS FINANCIAL INSTRUMENTS.

THE

