OTHER PROCEEDINGS

FROM TIME TO TIME, THE COMPANY IS INVOLVED IN PROCEEDINGS ADDRESSING DISPUTES WITH ITS REINSURERS REGARDING THE COLLECTION OF AMOUNTS DUE UNDER THE COMPANY'S

REINSURANCE AGREEMENTS. THESE PROCEEDINGS MAY BE INITIATED BY THE COMPANY OR THE REINSURERS AND MAY INVOLVE THE TERMS OF THE REINSURANCE AGREEMENTS, THE COVERAGE OF PARTICULAR CLAIMS, EXCLUSIONS UNDER

THE AGREEMENTS, AS WELL AS COUNTERCLAIMS FOR RESCISSION OF THE AGREEMENTS. ONE OF THESE DISPUTES IS THE ACTION DESCRIBED IN THE FOLLOWING PARAGRAPHS.

THE

