PLAN

AND, TO THE EXTENT SUCH SHARES BECAME AVAILABLE AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2005, THEY ARE INCLUDED IN THE TABLE AS AVAILABLE FOR GRANT: (I) SHARES COVERED BY OUTSTANDING AWARDS UNDER THE

